  <article id="section-simple-dialogs">
    <section class="app-section">
      <h2 class="hca-typography--title">Simple Dialogs</h2>
      <div class="row app-section">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <div class="hca-layout__container--body-content">
            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Simple Dialogs are called "simple" simply because they only take one action to move on from.</p>
            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">They present multiple options to the user, and close immediately upon the user making their selection. They should only be utilized in scenarios where the user is making a single selection from multiple options, and there is no further exploration to be made about these options.</p>
            <p class="hca-typography--support">NOTE: Simple Dialogs may have a "cancel" button as to provide a clear option for the user to dismiss, but they should not have any confirmation button. The user's selection immediately confirms their choice or executes the action.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
          <figure class="hca-visual-example">
            <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/dialogs/simple-dialog.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="Visual example of an Alert with no title" />
            <figcaption class="hca-visual-example__caption hca-typography--caption">A simple dialog</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="">
        <h3 class="hca-typography--body-2">Text options with varying heights</h3>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-5">
            <div class="hca-layout__container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Simple dialogs may present options in a text-only format. These options can vary in height, allowing for line breaking.</p>
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">It is still best to stay as concise as possible with these options. Try to avoid breaking more than three lines of text.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2">
            <figure class="hca-visual-example">
              <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/dialogs/simple-dialog-multi-line-text-options.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="A simple dialog with text options that vary in height" />
              <figcaption class="hca-visual-example__caption hca-typography--caption">A simple dialog with text options that vary in height.</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
